cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SD, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): This paper analyzes sentiment in text, specifically in the use of emoji. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The dataset used in this paper is based on comments made by employees of different companies, which can be seen as a social network. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society): The focus of this paper is on the impact of emoji use on the happiness of authors, which can be seen as a societal issue. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering): The methodology used in this paper involves building a sentiment benchmark, which can be seen as a software engineering task. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The sentiment analysis in this paper involves using machine learning techniques to compare the sentiment of writers and readers.
